    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>制作自己的波霸奶茶配方</strong></h2>让我们找出最好的配方。配方越好，顾客就越多来你的店里。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/eab3d7fb40a1c20e77e60071949a74a0.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>升级店铺和添加额外配料</strong></h2>选择在哪里花费你的收入。每次升级都会以自己的方式帮助你更快地成长。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/c4750d6a936ef69e1a7de98b292b9c97.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>管理库存和储存空间</strong></h2>你可以从超市购买波霸奶茶的原料。购买的数量越多，价格就越好。请记住你有限的储存空间。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/6a01633e6a0da752c6b203df0887c833.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>雇佣员工帮助你</strong></h2>员工可以极大地提高你的销售业绩。从候选人名单中选择你想要雇佣的人。你可以支付招聘机构获取专业候选人名单。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/2c138bba48f90ab85fecd659535cab81.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁新分店</strong></h2>解锁新分店将为你提供访问新店铺功能的权限。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.poster.avif?t=1758380127\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.webm?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1847510/extras/63d8f143a23d7a26838973d67de8ff4d.mp4?t=1758380127\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
